snippet.title: Quake - Undiscovered Technology of the Pharaohs
snippet.description:
Undiscovered Technology of the Pharaohs is an Egypt/techbase themed map pack using the Alkaline mod.

Slipseer page: https://www.slipseer.com/index.php?resources/undiscovered-technology-of-the-pharaohs.311/

Direct download: https://quakeworld.fi/files/zigi/utotp.zip

Music track "Cthonaut" by hotwheeis.
Check out hotweeis at:
https://soundcloud.com/hotwheeis
